Title: Non-standard neutrino interactions in K^{+}	o\pi^{+}
u ar{
u} and
  D^{+}	o\pi^{+}
u ar{
u} decays Abstract: We study the contributions of the non-standard neutrino interactions (NSIs)
to the rare meson decays of $K^{+}	o \pi^{+} 
u ar{
u}$ and $D^{+}	o
\pi^{+} 
u ar
u$. We show that both decays could provide strong constraints
on the free parameters in the NSIs. We point out that the branching ratio of
$D^{+}	o \pi^{+} 
u ar
u$ could be at the level of $10^{-8}$.
